data.description: This 4-bedroom home, featuring a newer roof (2017), Brand New AC, and water heater (2023), is a hidden gem on a spacious 9-acre property just minutes from the Suncoast. It boasts a saltwater pool with a new pump (2022) and a welcoming wrap-around porch. But that's not all! There are two detached garages, one of them a spacious 30x30 with water and a bathroom. This garage is perfect for storing farm equipment or creating a dream workshop.The property also comes with a solidly built barn, offering 7 stalls (12x12 each), feed and tack rooms, and two wash racks. Each stall is equipped with individual electrical outlets for fans, muscle stimulators, or grooming tools. In/out stalls lead to paddocks for easy animal access. The property is cross-fenced into 6 paddocks, simplifying trailer access and animal movement. There's even an RV 220amp hookup for added convenience.Privacy is ensured with a gated entrance, and the property's location at the end of the road creates a peaceful environment. For horse enthusiasts, this location is ideal, being within 50 miles of the World Equestrian Center in Ocala and offering multiple nearby riding trails.Despite its rural setting, this property remains close to shopping, dining, and entertainment options. It's the perfect blend of amenities, privacy, and convenience. Schedule a viewing and experience the 'WOW' factor for yourself!
